text: Surakshya Panta () is a Nepalese actress and model. She made her acting debut as an actress in Alok Nembang's Ajhai Pani in a supporting role. Panta received popularity after her role in Dhanapati. == References == == Other websites == * Category:Nepalese movie actors Category:Nepalese models Category:1992 births Category:Living people
